---
const sections = [
  {
    title: "目前持仓",
    category: "持仓记录",
    desc: "记录当前持仓列表、持仓状态和后续观察重点。具体仓位和成本可按需要逐步补充。",
    link: "/holdings/",
    cta: "查看持仓"
  },
  {
    title: "投资报告分析",
    category: "投研分析",
    desc: "整理投资报告、行业观察和对持仓逻辑的理解，方便把研究过程沉淀下来。",
    link: "/reports/",
    cta: "查看报告"
  },
  {
    title: "历史持仓收益",
    category: "收益复盘",
    desc: "复盘过去持仓区间的表现，记录收益、回撤、主要贡献和需要改进的地方。",
    link: "/history/",
    cta: "查看收益"
  }
];
---

<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>398的美股策略</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />

    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: Arial, "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
        background: #f5f7fb;
        color: #1f2937;
      }

      header {
        background-image:
          linear-gradient(
            rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.65),
            rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.75)
          ),
          url("/images/hero-bg.jpg");
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        color: white;
        padding: 56px 10% 72px;
      }

      nav {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: 72px;
      }

      .logo {
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
      }

      nav a {
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        margin-left: 28px;
        font-weight: 600;
        opacity: 0.92;
      }

      nav a:hover {
        opacity: 1;
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      .hero {
        max-width: 820px;
      }

      .site-title {
        font-size: 46px;
        line-height: 1.25;
        font-weight: 900;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .subtitle {
        font-size: 19px;
        line-height: 1.9;
        opacity: 0.95;
      }

      .tags {
        margin-top: 26px;
      }

      .tag {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-right: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        padding: 8px 14px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16);
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      main {
        max-width: 1120px;
        margin: 56px auto;
        padding: 0 24px;
      }

      .intro,
      .subscribe-box {
        background: white;
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 30px;
        margin-bottom: 42px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 26px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
        line-height: 1.9;
      }

      .intro h1,
      .subscribe-box h2 {
        font-size: 28px;
        margin-top: 0;
      }

      .intro p,
      .subscribe-box p {
        color: #4b5563;
      }

      .section-title {
        font-size: 28px;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      .grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(290px, 1fr));
        gap: 24px;
      }

      .card {
        background: white;
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 28px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 26px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
        transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
      }

      .card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-4px);
        box-shadow: 0 14px 36px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);
      }

      .category {
        display: inline-block;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #1d4ed8;
        font-weight: 800;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      .card h2 {
        font-size: 24px;
        line-height: 1.45;
        margin: 8px 0 10px;
      }

      .card p {
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: #4b5563;
      }

      .card-link {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 18px;
        color: #1d4ed8;
        font-weight: 800;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .card-link:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      .subscribe-box {
        margin-top: 54px;
        margin-bottom: 0;
      }

      .subscribe-form {
        display: flex;
        gap: 12px;
      }

      .subscribe-form input[type="email"] {
        flex: 1;
        min-width: 0;
        padding: 12px 14px;
        border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
        border-radius: 10px;
        color: #1f2937;
        font-size: 16px;
      }

      .subscribe-form button {
        padding: 12px 18px;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 10px;
        background: #2563eb;
        color: white;
        cursor: pointer;
        font-weight: 800;
      }

      .subscribe-form button:hover {
        background: #1d4ed8;
      }

      .disclaimer {
        margin-top: 54px;
        background: #eef2ff;
        border-left: 5px solid #2563eb;
        border-radius: 14px;
        padding: 22px 26px;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: #374151;
      }

      footer {
        text-align: center;
        color: #6b7280;
        padding: 42px 20px;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      @media (max-width: 700px) {
        header {
          padding: 36px 24px 56px;
        }

        nav {
          display: block;
          margin-bottom: 52px;
        }

        nav div:last-child {
          margin-top: 18px;
        }

        nav a {
          display: inline-block;
          margin-left: 0;
          margin-right: 18px;
          margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .site-title {
          font-size: 36px;
        }

        .subscribe-form {
          display: block;
        }

        .subscribe-form input[type="email"],
        .subscribe-form button {
          width: 100%;
          box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .subscribe-form button {
          margin-top: 12px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <header>
      <nav>
        <div class="logo">398的美股策略</div>
        <div>
          <a href="/">首页</a>
          <a href="/holdings/">目前持仓</a>
          <a href="/reports/">投资报告</a>
          <a href="/history/">历史收益</a>
          <a href="#subscribe">订阅</a>
        </div>
      </nav>

      <section class="hero">
        <div class="site-title">398的美股策略</div>
        <div class="subtitle">
          记录美股持仓、投资报告、持仓理解和历史收益复盘。
        </div>

        <div class="tags">
          <span class="tag">目前持仓</span>
          <span class="tag">投资报告分析</span>
          <span class="tag">历史持仓收益</span>
          <span class="tag">长期跟踪</span>
        </div>
      </section>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section class="intro">
        <h1>网站说明</h1>
        <p>
          这里主要用来整理个人投研记录。首页只放入口，具体内容会分到不同栏目里，
          以后内容变多后，每个栏目都可以继续按页展示。
        </p>
      </section>

      <h1 id="sections" class="section-title">内容板块</h1>

      <section class="grid">
        {sections.map((section) => (
          <article class="card">
            <div class="category">{section.category}</div>
            <h2>{section.title}</h2>
            <p>{section.desc}</p>
            <a class="card-link" href={section.link}>{section.cta} →</a>
          </article>
        ))}
      </section>

      <section id="subscribe" class="subscribe-box">
        <h2>订阅更新</h2>
        <p>输入邮箱后，后续发布新的持仓记录、投资报告或收益复盘时，可以收到邮件更新。</p>

        <form
          action="https://buttondown.com/api/emails/embed-subscribe/yufang"
          method="post"
          target="_blank"
          class="subscribe-form"
        >
          <input
            type="email"
            name="email"
            id="bd-email"
            placeholder="请输入你的邮箱"
            required
          />
          <input type="hidden" name="embed" value="1" />
          <button type="submit">订阅</button>
        </form>
      </section>

      <section class="disclaimer">
        <strong>风险提示：</strong>
        本网站内容仅为个人记录和学习复盘，不构成任何投资建议，也不作为买入、
        卖出或持有任何证券的依据。投资有风险，入市需谨慎。
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
      © 2026 398的美股策略 ｜ 个人投研记录，不构成投资建议
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
